+     install instructions for projects                   +
+                              projectstatistics          + 
+                              projectbilling             +
+                              projectdelivery            +          
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+            install the database tables                  +
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

create_tables.mysql [ can be found in projects-directory ]

command: mysql -uusername -ppassword dbname < create_tables.mysql

lang.sql & de_translation.sql 
[ can be found in each project*-directory ]

command: mysql -uusername -ppassword dbname < lang.sql
command: mysql -uusername -ppassword dbname < de_translation.sql

you have to replace 'username' with your db-user-name,
'password' with your db-users-password and 'dbname' with the
phpgroupware-db-name

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+                    project Admin                        +
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

create a group 'projectAdmin'
each member of this group is able to edit or delete all 
created projects

also the chosen coordinator of a project is able to manage 
his project 

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+                    management                           +
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
in it's current state is the projects-app required for 
running the other apps
projecthours is now included in projects and manages the 
daily jobs
projectbilling is needed to create invoices
projectstatistics creates user- and projectstats
projectdelivery manages delivery notes 
